---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Executive Coaching - ROM Business Psychology">

<!-- HERO WITH IMAGE -->
<section class="relative h-[50vh] min-h-[400px] flex items-center overflow-hidden">
  <img
    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573497019940-1c28c88b4f3e?w=1920&q=80"
    alt="Executive coaching session"
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
  />
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-900/90 via-indigo-900/70 to-transparent"></div>
  
  <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-6 max-w-[896px]">
    <p class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
      People
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-white text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
      Executive<br/>Coaching
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
      Managers rarely have 'just another day at the office.' Every day comes with surprises, crises, and questions that don't have easy answers.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- QUOTE BANNER -->
<section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 py-10">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-[896px]">
    <blockquote class="text-center">
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white font-light italic">
        "Even the most seasoned managers seek a partner with whom they can conduct a clarified dialogue."
      </p>
    </blockquote>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PARTNERSHIP -->
<section class="bg-white py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-[896px]">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="text-indigo-600 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Our Approach</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Bringing Partnership to the Table</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          The purpose of executive coaching is to provide managers with insights regarding their inner and outer surroundings through a series of one-on-one sessions.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Leaders get the opportunity to discuss their concerns, analyze and develop new approaches, formulate behavioral practices and assimilate managerial routines.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 to-purple-50 rounded-3xl p-10">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">What You Gain</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">New Insights</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Fresh perspectives on challenges</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Concrete Steps</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Actionable plans for current issues</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Future Infrastructure</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Tools for upcoming challenges</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PROCESS -->
<section class="bg-slate-900 py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-[896px]">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <p class="text-indigo-400 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">The Journey</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">How It Works</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-indigo-500/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-indigo-400">1</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Discuss</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Share concerns and challenges in a safe space</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-400">2</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Analyze</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Develop new approaches and perspectives</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-indigo-500/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-indigo-400">3</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Implement</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Formulate and assimilate new habits</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<Footer />
</Layout>
